name: Morning Ride
description:
fine art print on paper 9" by 18" $45
giclee print on canvas 12" by 24" $200

"Morning Ride"

This piece was commissioned by the town of Pemberton for use as a Street Banner. I painted it with the intention of capturing that amazing feeling of riding mountain bikes in our beautiful backyard of Pemberton B.C. 
The spectacular view of Mt Currie is featured complimented by a breathtaking sunrise.
I've been in this very spot, riding beneath magical trees, through the lush green and between the wildflowers.
I love where I live!
